<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset='utf-8'>
    <title>Word Counter</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Word Counter</h1>
    <br>
    <p>Enter a phrase and a word to search for in the boxes below. The program will then tell you how many times that word appears in the phrase.</p>
    <h3>Add Your Chosen Phrase And Word:</h3>
    <form action="/wordcounter" method="post">
      <label for="phrase">Phrase:</label>
      <input id="phrase" name="phrase" type="text" required>
      <br>
      <label for="word">Word:</label>
      <input id="word" name="word" type="text" required>
      <br>
      <br>
      <button type="submit">Submit Form</button>
    </form>
    <br>
    <br>
    <div class="container">
      <img src='~/img/snowdeer.jpg'>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
